metadata.name: The Harbor
metadata.description:
Welcome to the new land, with streets of gold and a sky of... strawberry lemonade?

One of the entries in my "Colorblindfull" collection. They are all color-shifted photos, seen through the eyes of someone who doesn't see the world in the same way most people do.

As this is my first mint in Foundation, I'm going to make it a 1/1. Don't lose your chance to own this!
